## How to Test
1. Open **Settings > Components > Drivers** and check the new "Installed" filter.
2. Try launching an Epic game; it should now correctly find its files and start in the right folder.
3. Try launching a Steam game in ColdClientLoader mode; the "Exe not found" error should be resolved.
4. Change the "Executable Path" for any game in its settings and verify it now persists and targets the correct file on the next launch.
